svg.text: Spin Game Discount Prizes won, are automatically applied to purchase, or saved in User’s account for later purchase of the same product unless otherwise stated on Discount prize details. Prizes not shipped By Spin Shopper will be automatically be exchanged for Store credit after 30 days from date issued.User’s are responsible for all, Duties, storage, and or and other fees associated after 14 days from date of winning prizePrizes are shipped from Canadian Location, prizes shipped outside of Canada maybe subject to customs fees which would be the Winner’s expense
